# Professional Portfolio Website

## Overview

This project is a professional portfolio website developed to present my qualifications, work experience, and technical skills.

The website combines business administration expertise with modern web development to create a structured and professional online presence.

This portfolio demonstrates both administrative knowledge and technical ability.

---

## Author

Refilwe Nkuna  
Business Management & Office Administration Professional

---

## Purpose

The purpose of this website is to:

- Present professional qualifications
- Showcase work experience
- Demonstrate technical skills
- Provide a professional online presence
- Allow employers to contact me

---

## Features

- Professional profile presentation
- Work experience section
- Skills and expertise section
- Project portfolio
- Contact form
- CV download option
- Mobile responsive design

---

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

---

